name: Zoo lift
description:
This is a socially symbolic AR Art for the action near the Kharkiv Zoo 2021, illustrates the relationship of man to man through animals. Full information on the website:
Crash elevator link: http://vlasbelov.tilda.ws/page21575746.html Millions of people every day use an elevator. For 5 minutes they get into the "cage" and before you go to the zoo to look at animals in captivity, remember this!
